Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要和自己的舌頭告別了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼發現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 這麼模糊的畫面實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在看什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\fn@微軟正黑體\frz270\pos(523,91)}同日上午
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白 小白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天發現了很糟糕的影像哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三科 你還真喜歡這種東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對色情影像可沒什麼興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這次不一樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天給你看的色情影像沒有告訴過雪染同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒說過啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之你快看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是很像小白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你如果做了壞事就快去自首去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三科
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有點在意這個跟我很像的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能傳給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是從三科那要來的不可思議影像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒…三科他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是不好找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很閒的話就過來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰說我很閒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這影像來看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪時間是 12月7日23時45分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地點是西蒲區比良坂大樓的屋頂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淡島副室長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道他的所在了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葦中學園…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學園島嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在城裡流傳的那段影像上的顯示日期是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12月7日晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,23時45分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算一下學校到犯罪現場的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一小時之內是無法趕到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能證明 7日的23時45分前後一小時內
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我人是在學校內的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的不在場證明就能成立了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你住的是單人房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人在房裡睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可不算不在場證明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的證詞我是不會認同的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小黑你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從遇到小白後我們就一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾輩的小白是好小白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 我說過不會相信你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道你也有參與的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會放過你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天因為要準備文化祭晚上也能留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛才想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天發生了很多事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以絕對…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人能證明我曾在那裡出現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們想邊換衣服邊聊天到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好合適啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白一點都不胖竟然那麼適合扮惠比壽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是珍貴的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾輩妹妹果然是個美人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾輩乃是美人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以問一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於12月7日的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是學園島的學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:10:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏是在這種不容易出手的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管他的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小八田…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪染菊理同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從見到你的那一刻我就愛上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的戀情結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾發生過那樣的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要重提那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宛若轉瞬消逝的煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.19,0:11:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時可真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間應該是午夜之前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是23時45分左右
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定是在那附近目睹那件事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這樣說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺你好像在又好像不在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這回答太模糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時怎麼會心情去管你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙想把文化祭用的煙火全部放完嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快找人把他抓下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 學生會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把門拆了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝進去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該是在現場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問你有印象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:11:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了要拖那個笨蛋下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間去注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候真是很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果會長沒有迅速地處理的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後果真是不堪設想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要看看那天的報導嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:18.05,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz342.335\move(281,100,324,-48,0,980)}夜空綻放的　　之花!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:18.05,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz318.919\move(292,104,329,-25,0,900)}失戀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有拍到我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要騷動時有無拍到自己照片的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如去問看看新聞部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那晚他們可是拍了不少照片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那之後不斷發生的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是有會長妥善的處理才能解決
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些活躍的鏡頭應該也有拍下來才對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說現在是文化祭的準備階段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不能穿著這麼奇怪的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在校園裡走動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過長的道具是禁止攜帶的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才不是什麼道具…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰快拿滅火器來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰來把馬攔住呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這氣勢真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可別漏掉精彩畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明記得我在這附近走動的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天的照片數量非常多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果在附近的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總會有一張拍到你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙果然沒有不在場證明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 什麼不在場證明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是什麼頭條新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 沒什麼事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是困擾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}不勝感激 x 2 不勝感激喵x 2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}莫戲弄僕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}真是辛苦喵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為一定有的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是小白你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的大家都在忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要搬去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那幫我搬到教員室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}制裁 x 2 非常抱歉 x 2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}到達
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把這個拿去學生會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教員室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先放在那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學生的外出記錄？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,校門口的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是可以 但理由呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有什麼大事啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我快要被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要什麼時候的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12月7日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 7日的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有澤 有吉 飯田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊久的後面是井上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 沒有伊佐那社吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白 小白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾輩肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能證明我是清白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hungry！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來去吃些點心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點心點心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說到點心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊理說她會拿好吃的仙貝來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且她朋友還說要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買好吃的大福給我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白 買點喝的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進出這座小島的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都會通過自動門的檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個會「嗶嗶」響的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這份名單沒有我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就證明我一直待在島上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:18.15,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,385)}可以用 Sui 來支付唷♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:18.15,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Suica︰是一款能在東京圈範圍內用於乘車、購物的預付費式電子貨幣。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能去犯罪現場的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾輩要果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 零錢不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又沒帶手機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是規定 要好好帶著才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且沒帶也很不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙都不帶手機的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管說多少次他都會忘記呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不帶終手機的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就無法通過大門了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這人總會耍小聰明偷溜出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:17:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在這裡會發生一些令人不舒服的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去旁邊一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始我會認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認真的找證據
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經很清楚到你是一個不誠實的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這傢伙的同夥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算與主人同生共死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾輩是貓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小白的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會把小白交給小黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白那麼溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還會跟我一起吃飯和點心的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓 貓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣只會令事情更難辦的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 狗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始我會好好找證據的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一天發生了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如噴水池破壞事件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廁所淹水事件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,體育館倉庫天花板崩落事件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定有出現在某個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天我記得在體育館倉庫有見過小白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從…三科同學那裡逃離後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.46,0:18:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和小白一起發現了這個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得那是幾點的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12點半哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在犯罪時間1小時之內
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要在這時間之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從犯罪現場趕回來是不可能的…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次不在場證明終於成立了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在說你是我的救命恩人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要拖拖拉拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離文化祭沒多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了狗朗幫忙之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}別說話了 快動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作效率大大提高了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.68,0:19:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連轉學生狗朗都這麼努力說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙又不見人影了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個 真的是轉學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累死了 累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:20:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連幾天都被追殺真是受不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制服忘在教室裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唷 真是美好的夜晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是來拍攝這夜景的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫十束多多良
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.57,0:20:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是第七王權者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無色之王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在這裡等人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說是很好的夜晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 的確是個美好的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.78,0:21:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是要吃點心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊理給我超辣仙貝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以讓我來叫小白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫完小白後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會再給我超辣仙貝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 現在就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子痛…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.67,0:21:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不勝感激
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個混蛋就在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.30,0:22:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就去把你大卸八塊
